data.title: Alumni Annual 2010
data.meta_description: alumni_annual_2010 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides an overview of the LUMS Alumni Annual Magazine. It includes messages from the Alumni Affairs Office, Pro Chancellor, and Vice Chancellor welcoming alumni and highlighting LUMS' growth over 25 years. The magazine contents section lists articles on change management, entrepreneurship, and career experiences. It also previews interviews and updates on LUMS schools, student societies, outreach programs, and alumni events. The document encourages alumni to stay engaged with LUMS and support its continued progress.
